title: Zeit Boy Rick 3/5: The Wire, Supreme Air Force 1, Art Van, The Last of Us
itunes:title: Zeit Boy Rick 3/5: The Wire, Supreme Air Force 1, Art Van, The Last of Us
description:
On this edition of Zeit Boy Rick Jack and Miles (and DJ Danl) discuss whether the Wire or Breaking Bad is better, Supreme is working with Nike on a new Air Force 1, Art Van is closing down, and a Last of Us show is in development.
